x4freetext: Measured by unfolding multi-foil activation for
Ni-58(n,p), Al-27(n,p) reactions, ENDF/B-V data were
used ( 144 energy groups from 0.01 eV to 16.4 MeV).
Epithermal region was measured by In-115, Au-197,
Most samples are metallic foils of 12.7 mm diameter,
Ga and Na were prepared by absorption of the aqueous
solution into filter paper and drying.
The sample and Au foils with Cd-cover were stuck on
Al holder and set in the center of internal graphite
